description:
On March 8, 2013, Randy Brecker visited UW-Eau Claire. Brecker, a five-time Grammy Award-winning jazz trumpeter held a clinic at Haas Fine Arts Center. He also performed with a small jazz combo which included UW-Eau Claire students. One of those students, Mike Malone, was later chosen to be the new drummer for the Glenn Miller Orchestra as it tours the world.
